Global Montanic Acid Methyl Ester Market Insights
Montanic Acid Methyl Ester Market size was valued at USD 0.5 Billion in 2022 and is projected to reach USD 0.8 Billion by 2030, growing at a CAGR of 7.5% from 2024 to 2030.

Montanic Acid Methyl Ester Market Overview
The Montanic Acid Methyl Ester market has experienced significant growth, driven by its expanding use in industries such as personal care, plastics, and coatings. As of 2024, the market value is estimated at USD 1.2 billion, with a projected compound annual growth rate (CAGR) of 5.6% from 2025 to 2030. The growth is primarily attributed to the rising demand for eco-friendly and sustainable alternatives in various applications, particularly in biodegradable products. Additionally, the increased awareness of environmental concerns and the shift towards green chemistry have further fueled the market’s expansion.

